Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:01.50,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.53,0:00:02.86,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,How are the repairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.77,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,I’m almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:09.00,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,The battery will be fully\Ncharged in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:10.23,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:11.80,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,what are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:14.83,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,This is, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:18.73,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,This is the true form of the\Nenergy coming from the meteor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:23.33,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,But I’ve never seen\Nanything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:28.66,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,I don’t know where\Nthis energy came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:32.73,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,But if Wily gets a hold of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:34.37,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,It’s dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:35.66,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,You must recover\Nthem immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:39.00,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,But, where is Wily?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:44.43,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,Maybe there are other\Nenergy readings as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:46.77,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,Let’s try retracting\Nit in the radar room
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:49.40,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,It’s possible Wily still has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:45.61,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,He’s...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.53,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,He’s still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.03,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,That’s...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:00.90,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,Mega Man! Go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:04.46,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,Until we know who that robot is,\Nwe can’t leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:05.10,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:06.33,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Rush!
